Use Python coding best practices
Always maintain init.sh with python environment and requirements in an idempotent manner.
Create, update and maintain todo.txt with project milestones and associated tasks tracked with next steps.
Update the todo.txt after completing tasks.
Commit code when you complete milestones.
Create the test before writing the code.
Always search your codebase for similar functions before writing code or a new test.
Configure git so it executes tests before allowing Commit